# AI Cloud VM Migration Assistant

> Automated Infrastructure & Configuration Deployment Engine powered by **MiMo-V2.5-Pro**

[![CI](https://github.com/xiaomi-mimo/migration-assistant/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/xiaomi-mimo/migration-assistant/actions)
[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg)](LICENSE)
[![Python 3.10+](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.10+-blue.svg)](https://www.python.org/downloads/)

An autonomous AI agent that maps, configures, and executes server migration across cloud providers, bare-metal, WSL2, and mobile (Termux) environments. Powered by MiMo-V2.5-Pro for multi-step planning and shell script generation.

---

## Problem

Migrating AI infrastructure (Ollama, OpenClaw, API Gateways, GCP VMs) between servers is error-prone:

| Pain Point | Risk |
|---|---|
| `.env` files left behind or corrupted | Credential loss, broken services |
| Port binding conflicts | Downtime, debugging hell |
| OS differences (Ubuntu GCP → WSL2 → Termux) | Permission errors, path mismatches |
| Manual sequence of stop-copy-configure-start | Missed steps, partial failures |

## Solution

**Migration Assistant** is a CLI tool installed on both source and target machines. It acts as an autonomous infrastructure operator:

```
migrate plan --source user@host --target user@host
migrate execute --plan migration-20260522.json
migrate validate --plan migration-20260522.json
```

## Architecture

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    Migration Assistant CLI                   │
├─────────┬──────────┬───────────┬──────────┬─────────────────┤
│ Scraper │ Blueprint│ Credential│ Executor │   Validator     │
│  Node   │Generator │  Carrier  │  Engine  │   Lifecycle     │
├─────────┴──────────┴───────────┴──────────┴─────────────────┤
│              MiMo-V2.5-Pro Reasoning Core                   │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│            SSH / Local / Docker Transport Layer              │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Components

| Component | Role |
|---|---|
| **Environment Scraper** | Reads source machine: services, ports, configs, systemd units, docker containers |
| **Blueprint Generator** | MiMo analyzes telemetry → generates ordered bash migration script |
| **Credential Carrier** | Encrypts & transfers `.env`, SSL certs, API keys without leaking to logs |
| **Executor Engine** | Runs migration steps sequentially with rollback on failure |
| **Validator Lifecycle** | Health-checks every service post-migration, reports status |
| **Notifier** | Sends migration report to Telegram/Slack/webhook |

## Quick Start

```bash
# Install
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# Plan a migration
migrate plan \
  --source ssh://root@old-server \
  --target ssh://root@new-server \
  --services ollama,openclaw,api-gateway \
  --output plan.json

# Execute (with confirmation prompts)
migrate execute --plan plan.json --confirm

# Validate
migrate validate --plan plan.json
```

## Key Features

- **Zero-downtime migration**: Services stopped only during actual file transfer
- **Credential safety**: AES-256 encryption for secrets, never logged in plaintext
- **OS-aware**: Detects Ubuntu/Debian/WSL2/Termux and adapts paths, permissions, package managers
- **Port conflict detection**: Scans target before migration, suggests alternative ports
- **Rollback**: Automatic rollback on any step failure
- **Telegram reporting**: Real-time migration status updates

## MiMo-V2.5-Pro Leverage

This project specifically exploits MiMo's strengths:

1. **Coding Benchmark Leader** (ClawEval/GDPVal-AA): Generates syntactically perfect bash scripts across OS variants
2. **Multi-Step Planning**: Maintains strict ordering of migration steps (stop → compress → transfer → configure → start → validate)
3. **Environment Reasoning**: Reads complex system telemetry and identifies hidden dependencies between services

## Project Structure

```
mimo-migration-assistant/
├── src/mimo_migration_assistant/
│   ├── cli/              # CLI entry points
│   ├── scraper/          # Source machine environment scanner
│   ├── blueprint/        # MiMo-powered migration plan generator
│   ├── credential/       # Encrypted secret transfer
│   ├── executor/         # Step-by-step execution engine
│   ├── validator/        # Post-migration health checks
│   ├── notifier/         # Telegram/webhook notifications
│   ├── models/           # Data models (Service, MigrationPlan, etc.)
│   └── utils/            # SSH, encryption, OS detection helpers
├── tests/
├── docs/
├── examples/
└── scripts/
```

